<template>
  <basic-unit class="fishingUnit" @click="update">
    <slot></slot>
  </basic-unit>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props:['fishName'],
  methods: {
    update(){
      this.$emit('update-selected',this.fishName)
    }
  },

}
</script>

<style>
    .fishingUnit :deep(.basicUnit){
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>
